# Frontend Component Patterns

## Component Structure
- Use `src/app/components/` for layout (Header, Nav, Footer) and shared UI
- Functional components with hooks only; define props interface above component
- Destructure props at the function signature; use Tailwind for styling
- Follow design tokens (CSS variables in globals.css); mobile-first responsive

## Styling
- Tailwind CSS; no inline styles except dynamic values
- Use semantic HTML and ARIA where needed; support dark mode via class
